name: beef stew
instructions:
1. In a Dutch oven or large pan, add olive oil and heat over medium heat.

2. Add beef roast and brown on all sides.

3. Mince garlic, slice onions and carrots, and add to hot pan. Allow to soften slightly.

4. Add red wine, canned tomatoes, stock, oregano and basil. Add salt and pepper to taste. 

5. Put lid on and simmer on low heat for at least one hour.
